        AMRecord represents the data fields that the user would store in a persistent data store.
        Parameters:
        svc - Service code such as session or saml2
        op - Operation such as read, write, delete, deletebydate.
        pKey - Primary Key
        eDate - Expiration Date
        secKey - Secondary Key
        st - state
        ax - Additional Data
        stringBlob - Data Blob
